{"id": "1330758228807647253", "channel_id": "1330758228807647253", "type": 0, "author_id": "694573382380945529", "author_name": "craux.", "author_bot": false, "content": "As for the current ranking system, I feel it's a bit painful for higher ranks. because when we lose, we get deducted like -170 point, but if we win we only get +60 or even worse +20ish. It took a long time to climb just to lose once and getting alot of minus.\n\nMaybe we can have a ranking system based on stars like:\n- Bronze 3 (need 3 stars to Bronze 2)\n- Bronze 2 ...\n- Bronze 1 ...\n- Silver 3 ...\n\nThis way it doesn't hurt for higher ranks because they only get -1 star for losing a game.", "timestamp": "2025-01-20T04:38:06.040000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1330758228807647253", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "traphase ranking system rework", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
